<Author>petehz
<Content>A Hidden Gem! I had a very bad experience at a nearby hotel and need a place to stay last minute. Not only were they very accommodating, but the rooms were a lot nicer than I thought. I reserved a jacuzzi suite which was very comfortable and actually less expensive than the regular guest rooms at nearby hotels, They are also are conveniently located less than 10 minutes from Base Ramey Internantional airport. We ate at the hotels restaurant and the food was very good- they serve mainly native dishes from the island. If your visiting the Aguadilla area of Puerto Rico, I highly recommend this hotel 
