<Author>Estrelitatraveling
<Content>Truly a paradise!!!!! My family decided on a trip to PR and couldn't decide on a hotel so I randomly chose this one. We were so surprised to find this oasis in the middle of aguadilla! The service was superb, they couldn't do enough for us . The price was so decent we stood 4 extra days and still didn't break our budget. the rooms were so clean and the maids(especially Vicky) were on top of everything yet never invaded our privacy. The grounds are so nice and pure looking. The front desk personel was imformative and told us many places that we could visit. We were taken to the airport on a shuttle and we were treated like royalty. I do ALOT of traveling and I can honestly say this is one of the best hotel stays I've had in a very long time. My family decided we are going to have our family reunion at the Pedregal next year! Don't miss out on this paradise!!! 
